Police are looking for a man who allegedly killed his wife after an argument in Riruta area, Nairobi, on Sunday night.The suspect identified as Benson Mwaura is said to have escaped from his house after the murder.Officers said Mwaura used a knife and metal rod to attack the woman in their bedroom before fleeing.Neighbours said the two had disagreed often.Cases of tragic domestic squabbles have been on the rise across the county, common reasons being infidelity and lack of children.Read: End the horror at home now